summary: An Ordinance providing for the of cost and expense of laying off, opening, extending and establishing of an alley over and across certain unplatted land adjoining block five (5) of Pettit-Brown's Lakeview Addition to the City of Seattle, on the south, and over and across Lot One (1), Block One (1), of C. P. Dose's Lake Washington Addition to the City of Seattle, by the issuance and sale of bonds of the district created to pay therefor.
